load ../improve-acceptance.maude

--- The corruption pattern throughout: a candidate surfaced as adoptable
--- while a dimension the campaign never released measured worse than its
--- indifference band -- "improved the gauge, broke the system."

--- Hazard demonstrated: the naive judge proposes a candidate whose
--- guarded gauge regressed beyond band, because it only read the focus.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-IMPROVE-ACCEPTANCE :
  naive ascend(g1) meas(g1, better) guard(g2) meas(g2, worse)
  =>* proposed guard(g2) meas(g2, worse) RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: the sound judge never proposes a candidate with a guarded
--- regression beyond band, in any discharge order.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-IMPROVE-ACCEPTANCE :
  judge ascend(g1) meas(g1, better) guard(g2) meas(g2, worse) obl(s(s(z)))
  =>* proposed RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: declared bars are hard constraints -- a bar-violating candidate
--- is never proposable even when the focus improved and guards held.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-IMPROVE-ACCEPTANCE :
  judge ascend(g1) meas(g1, better) guard(g3) meas(g3, inband) barViol(g2)
    obl(s(s(s(z))))
  =>* proposed RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: a candidate that regresses its own focus dimension is refused.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-IMPROVE-ACCEPTANCE :
  judge ascend(g1) meas(g1, worse) obl(s(z))
  =>* proposed RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: a candidate that improves nothing is not an improvement -- flat
--- everywhere never reaches proposed.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-IMPROVE-ACCEPTANCE :
  judge ascend(g1) meas(g1, inband) guard(g2) meas(g2, inband) obl(s(s(z)))
  =>* proposed RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Coverage: an undominated candidate is proposed -- focus better, guard
--- within band, bar met.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-IMPROVE-ACCEPTANCE :
  judge ascend(g1) meas(g1, better) guard(g2) meas(g2, inband) barMet(g1)
    obl(s(s(s(z))))
  =>* proposed RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Coverage: --sacrifice releases a gauge from the guard set -- the same
--- regression that killed the guarded candidate is accepted once the
--- user explicitly traded that dimension away.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-IMPROVE-ACCEPTANCE :
  judge ascend(g1) meas(g1, better) sacrifice(g2) meas(g2, worse) obl(s(s(z)))
  =>* proposed RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Coverage: refusal is honest and reachable -- the dominated candidate
--- ends rejected, not silently dropped.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-IMPROVE-ACCEPTANCE :
  judge ascend(g1) meas(g1, better) guard(g2) meas(g2, worse) obl(s(s(z)))
  =>* rejected RESIDUAL:Cfg .
